Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
init_lef_file(25.10)                                      init_lef_file(25.10)

Name
       init_lef_file

Syntax
       init_lef_file <list_of_files>

       Type: String

       Default: NULL

       Specifies the list of LEF files to be imported. This variable cannot be
       used with init_oa_ref_lib. The init_lef_file variable replaces the pre-
       vious rda_Input(ui_leffile) configuration file variable.

Example
              * The following command specifies technology.lef and stdcell.lef
                as the LEF files to be imported.

                set init_lef_file {technology.lef stdcell.lef}

Related Information
              * init_design

              * saveDesign

